headline: MNTN CEO on Apple Plans AI Search Tool for Siri
summary: Mark Douglas, MNTN CEO, says Apple has little choice but to develop an AI-powered web search tool for Siri to rival OpenAI. He tells Romaine Bostick and Katie Greifeld on "The Close" that Apple doesn't have a strong track record on execution.
